name: CompositeSet_containsTest
description: Unit tests for the contains method of the CompositeSet class.

test_cases.name: testContains_ElementInFirstSet
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeSet contains an element that is present in the first set.

test_cases.name: testContains_ElementInSecondSet
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeSet contains an element that is present in the second set.

test_cases.name: testContains_ElementNotInAnySet
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeSet does not contain an element that is not present in any set.

test_cases.name: testContains_NullElement
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeSet does not contain a null element.

test_cases.name: testContains_EmptyCompositeSet
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeSet does not contain an element when it is empty.

test_cases.name: testContains_ElementInBothSets
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeSet contains an element that is present in both sets.
